        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Go the library. Pick up any book. Find a page at random. Read the first paragraph you see.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Think it over.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Do you agree? Disagree?",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Why?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Does this relate to something you’ve read or seen or experienced?",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "How?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Any additional comments or criticisms?",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Even if you don’t understand the context, surely you have an opinion.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Everyone does.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Writing is merely the process of getting those thoughts out in a way that’s coherent and concise. Whether your style is technical or comedic, persuasive or poetic, descriptive or anecdotic, the purpose is the same.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The approach, the text, the style, it’s all secondary.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The point is to have a point of view, throughout.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}